Asset explore
-------------
You can borrow items from a foreigner (assets (accomodation/car/suplies) with public or friends visibility)
Assets can be filtered by capacity, availability, topic (very similar screen then the event explore)
Assets can have price tag (we haven't introduced purse for public/friends event also)

